### Variables
@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8000
@token = your_auth_token_here
@userId = 1

### ============================================
### AUTHENTICATION
### ============================================

### Get Auth Token (Login)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth-token/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "password": "your_password"
}

### OAuth Login - Google (redirect in browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/google/login/

### OAuth Login - GitHub (redirect in browser)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/github/login/

### OAuth Callback (handled automatically by allauth)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/google/login/callback/

### Logout
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/accounts/logout/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### ============================================
### USER MANAGEMENT - DRF API (REST)
### ============================================

### Register New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/register/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "newuser@example.com",
  "password": "securepassword123",
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "role": "user",
  "location": "New York"
}

### Get All Users (REST API - viewset)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Get Current User (Me)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Get Specific User by ID (REST API - viewset)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### Update User (REST API - viewset - PATCH)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token {{token}}

{
  "first_name": "Jane",
  "last_name": "Smith",
  "role": "admin",
  "location": "Los Angeles"
}

### Update User (REST API - viewset - PUT)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Token {{token}}

{
  "email": "user@example.com",
  "first_name": "Jane",
  "last_name": "Smith",
  "role": "admin",
  "location": "Los Angeles"
}

### Delete User
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/users/deleteUser/{{userId}}/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### ============================================
### USER MANAGEMENT - Django Views (non-API)
### ============================================

### User Detail (returns user data for specific ID)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/{{userId}}/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### User Redirect (redirects to user detail)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/~redirect/
Authorization: Token {{token}}

### User Update (Django form view)
# POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/~update/
# Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded
# Authorization: Token {{token}}
#
# name=Updated Name

### ============================================
### API SCHEMA & DOCUMENTATION
### ============================================

### Get OpenAPI Schema
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/schema/

### Open Swagger Documentation (in browser)
# GET {{baseUrl}}/api/docs/

